[04/07/2019 09:57:15] <font color="#ffffff">¡Guau!</font>
[04/07/2019 09:57:15] <font color="#ffffff">"...de emociones intensas".</font>
[04/07/2019 09:57:17] <font color="#ffffff">¡Qué desastre!</font>
[04/07/2019 09:57:17] <font color="#ffffff">¿No es genial?</font>
[04/07/2019 09:57:18] <font color="#ffffff">95.</font>
[04/07/2019 09:57:18] <font color="#ffffff">¡Boom!</font>
